gravitational constant at surface, make dependant on lat and lon (see read_ecmwf.f90 ll. 947ff.)

error handling if no argument is provided to download scripts

https://gitlab.iup.uni-heidelberg.de/atmo/remotec-oco-pre/-/blob/master/SRC/read_ecmwf.f90#L963
!*** Height profile
z_in(ilon,ilat,nlev+1,itime)=z_in(ilon,ilat,nlev+1,itime)/gE0
DO ilev=1,nlev
	z_in(ilon,ilat,ilev,itime)=-7.D3*DLOG(p_in(ilon,ilat,ilev,itime)/p_in(ilon,ilat,nlev+1,itime))+&
	z_in(ilon,ilat,nlev+1,itime)
ENDDO

